{"tid":1791898,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國幾時先肯放棄西曆，改用中曆，以中國有明確曆歷史紀年為第一年","createTime":"2019-12-21T08:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T08:32:38.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e04a36e6778085a4f51299e2fd462fa7b56cd1e","tid":1791898,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"成日鬧西方，話西方唔好，又鬧西方干預中國內政<br />\n又成日強調話要有中國特式<br />\n<br />\n咁用西曆/格里曆/耶穌曆/基督曆/主曆做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用中曆咪好<br />\n<br />\n嫌農曆太舊，唔好計的話，咪改革囉<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n以中國有明切紀年及連續歷史記錄，即共和元年(BCE 841)開始為第一年<br />\n<br />\n今年係2860年<br />\n<br />\n以立春為1月1日<br />\n<br />\n現在係中曆2860年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n中共敢做我實支持"},{"pid":"36b71decc2b12fea5eab8cba0a2ade904c7b2cfb","tid":1791898,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"共產70年xx月xx日"},{"pid":"58e3ee6001f43e8a523d7b8897e4c068c7fae5a7","tid":1791898,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"新中國曆，以立春為1月1日，以中國開始有明確紀年為第一年。<br />\n一來可以去宗教化，去神化。新曆法比較合乎「科學」和「歷史」。又可以向世界輸出中國文化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連曆法都唔敢用自己的，唔敢向世界推廣，就咪撚話自己係強國啦。"},{"pid":"252c26890236a9cb317f1cf5e6a083d51023200b","tid":1791898,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36b71decc2b12fea5eab8cba0a2ade904c7b2cfb","tid":1791898,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"共產70年xx月xx日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"不能輸出世界<br />\n改左朝代就無用"},{"pid":"ee1e45db02e47de22bd82b219d026e65ba8ffe6f","tid":1791898,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"習帝元年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db3b5dad5873c0074a4f44acef5462aa6c3d036","tid":1791898,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee1e45db02e47de22bd